sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant N as n8n
    participant G as Greenlight
    participant T as ntfy
    participant U as You (phone / web)

    N->>G: POST /api/requests<br/>(title, resume_url, timeout, …)
    G->>G: resolve default rule → store as pending
    G-->>N: 201 { id, url, status: pending }
    G->>T: publish notification (deep link)
    T-->>U: push

    alt You decide before the timeout
        U->>G: Approve / Reject (+ comment)
    else Timeout elapses
        G->>G: scheduler applies default action
    end

    G->>N: POST resume_url { decision, … }
    N->>N: continue workflow (approved / rejected branch)
